text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_WelcomeToLilycoveMuseum {
	"Welcome to LILYCOVE MUSEUM.

	Please take the time to enjoy our
	collection of fantastic artwork
	featuring POKéMON."
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_ImCuratorHaveYouViewedOurPaintings {
	"I'm the CURATOR of this MUSEUM of
	fine arts.

	It's heartening to see someone so
	young as you in our MUSEUM.

	Have you viewed our collection of
	paintings already?"
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_NotDisturbYouTakeYourTime {
	"Ah, then let me not disturb you.
	Please, do take your time."
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_HaveYouAnInterestInPaintings {
	"Oh? I do believe that you seem to
	be a POKéMON TRAINER.

	Have you an interest in paintings,
	too?"
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_HonoredYoudVisitInSpiteOfThat {
	"I see…

	I'm honored that you would visit
	us in spite of that."
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_ExcellentCanYouComeWithMe {
	"Ah, excellent!
	You do like paintings!

	Then, may I ask you to come with me?"
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_VeryOldPainting {
	"It's a very old painting.
	The paint is peeling here and there."
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_OddLandscapeFantasticScenery {
	"It's an odd landscape with bizarre
	and fantastic scenery."
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_PaintingOfBeautifulWoman {
	"It's a painting of a beautiful, smiling
	woman with a POKéMON on her lap."
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_PaintingOfLegendaryPokemon {
	"It's a painting of a legendary POKéMON
	from long ago.

	The artist painted this from
	imagination."
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_PaintingOfGrassPokemon {
	"It's a painting of GRASS POKéMON
	swaying in a breeze.

	They appear to be enjoying the wind's
	gentle caress."
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_PaintingOfBerries {
	"It's a delicious-looking painting
	of BERRIES.

	This painting could make you hungry!"
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_Text_BirdPokemonSculptureReplica {
	"It's a replica of a famous sculpture.

	It depicts an ancient BIRD POKéMON."
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_BigPokeBallCarvedFromStone {
	"It's a big POKé BALL carved from
	a black stone.

	It was apparently used in festivals
	in the olden days."
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_StoneTabletWithAncientText {
	"It's a huge stone tablet inscribed
	with POKéMON and dense text in the
	small characters of an ancient,
	unreadable language."
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_WorksOfMagnificence {
	"Hmmm…
	What works of great magnificence…"
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_MustntForgetLoveForFineArts {
	"Battling with POKéMON is fun,
	I'll grant you that.

	But one mustn't forget our love for
	the fine arts."
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_ThisMuseumIsInspiration {
	"This ART MUSEUM… Well, you could
	see many fantastic paintings.

	And the CURATOR is a wonderful person.

	Among artists like myself, this MUSEUM
	is an inspiration."
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_ThisLadyIsPretty {
	"This lady is pretty!
	She's like Mommy!"
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_ThisPokemonIsAdorable {
	"This POKéMON is adorable!
	Just like our little boy!"
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_HeardMuseumGotNewPaintings {
	"I'd heard that this ART MUSEUM got
	in some new paintings.

	So, naturally I hurried over.

	Are the new paintings up on
	the second floor?"
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_CuratorHasBeenCheerful {
	"Lately, the CURATOR has been
	unusually cheerful.

	I bet something good happened for him.
	Definitely."
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_AimToSeeGreatPaintings {
	"I aim to see many great paintings
	here and learn from them.

	I have this dream of one day having
	my artwork exhibited here."
}

text LilycoveCity_LilycoveMuseum_1F_Text_MuseumTouristDestination {
	"The ART MUSEUM has become a favorite
	tourist destination.

	It's great for LILYCOVE…
	No, great for the HOENN region!

	This is what I've heard--a lone TRAINER
	procured all the paintings upstairs."
}
